OL,3,CFatal accident inquiry to take place
OL,4,Cinto Borders teenager's death
OL,6,FA fatal accident inquiry is set to
OL,7,Ftake place following the death of a
OL,8,FBorders teenager.
OL,10,FHarris Macdonell was 19-years-old when
OL,11,Fhe took his own life after being
OL,12,Ftreated in an adult mental health unit.
OL,14,FHis mum, Jane Macdonell, says her son
OL,15,FHarris was "traumatised" after
OL,16,Freceiving treatment at' Huntlyburn
OL,17,FHouse and believes access to a young
OL,18,Fperson's mental health ward could have
OL,19,Fsaved his life.
