OL,6,FThe Lord Advocate has decided that a
OL,7,Ffatal accident inquiry is in the
OL,8,Fpublic interest regarding the
OL,9,Fcircumstances surrounding his death.
OL,11,FThe decision to hold an inquiry was
OL,12,Fmade following an independent
OL,13,Finvestigation by the Procurator Fiscal.
