OL,3,CFatal accident inquiry to take place
OL,4,Cinto Borders teenager's death
OL,6,FProcurator Fiscal Andy Shanks, who
OL,7,Fleads on fatalities investigations for
OL,8,FCrown Office and Procurator Fiscal
OL,9,FService, said: "The Lord Advocate has
OL,10,Fdecided that a discretionary Fatal
OL,11,FAccident Inquiry should be held into
OL,12,Fthe causes of this tragic death to
OL,13,Fensure that there can be a full public
OL,14,Fhearing of the facts of the case.
OL,16,F"The Procurator Fiscal has now started
OL,17,Fwork to initiate this inquiry and
OL,18,Fthere are a number of legal steps
OL,19,Fwhich must be taken before it can
OL,20,Fcommence.
