OL,3,CFatal accident inquiry to take place
OL,4,Cinto Borders teenager's death
OL,6,F"Harris' family will be kept informed
OL,7,Fof what will happen next."
OL,9,FA previous statement by NHS Borders
OL,10,Fsaid: "Whilst in order to respect
OL,11,Fconfidentiality we will not comment in
OL,12,Fdetail, we can confirm that following
OL,13,FHarris's tragic death an extensive and
OL,14,Fexternally led review of his care was
OL,15,Fundertaken so that we could learn any
OL,16,Flessons to improve our services in the
OL,17,Ffuture.
OL,19,F"The actions identified by the review
OL,20,Fhave been implemented.
