OL,4,Cinto Borders teenager's death
OL,6,F"We agree that children and young
OL,7,Fpeople who require inpatient care
OL,8,Fshould, wherever possible, be admitted
OL,9,Fto an age-appropriate unit.
OL,11,F"If this is not possible, and they
OL,12,Fhave to be admitted to our adult
OL,13,Finpatient unit, we will always advise
OL,14,Fthe Mental Welfare Commission (MWC)
OL,15,Fthat this has happened, in line with
OL,16,Ftheir guidance.
OL,18,F"Our practice is then informed by the
OL,19,FMWC for Scotland guidance on treating
OL,20,Fchildren and young people in adult
OL,21,Fmental health wards."
